<Link id="l00566" /><CodeLine lineNumber="566"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// grow the table.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00567" /><CodeLine lineNumber="567"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00568" /><CodeLine lineNumber="568"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The later case is tricky.  For example, if we had one empty bucket with</span></CodeLine>
